HEADWORD: Ethical
<hw>Eth"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
}</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>ethicus</ets>, Gr. <?/, fr. <?/
custom, usage, character, dwelling; akin to <?/ custom, Goth.
<ets>sidus</ets>, G. <ets>sitte</ets>, Skr. <ets>svadh<?/</ets>, prob.
orig., one's own doing; <ets>sva</ets> self + <ets>dh<?/</ets> to set:
